{
  "text": "(11) After the computation of the approximate Shapley value, we implement the process of balancing the total budget [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] to guarantee the efficiency axiom. The process uses sample averages and variances of the strata to find the maximum likelihood estimates of the Shapley value with budget constraints as follows:",
